mapper.insert: insert into rwlock_instances (OBJECT_INSTANCE_BEGIN, NAME, WRITE_LOCKED_BY_THREAD_ID, READ_LOCKED_BY_COUNT) values (#{objectInstanceBegin,jdbcType=BIGINT}, #{name,jdbcType=VARCHAR}, #{writeLockedByThreadId,jdbcType=BIGINT}, #{readLockedByCount,jdbcType=INTEGER})
mapper.select: select OBJECT_INSTANCE_BEGIN, NAME, WRITE_LOCKED_BY_THREAD_ID, READ_LOCKED_BY_COUNT from rwlock_instances
